{"tid":1860994,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"［An/iOS］三國志 英雄 Heroz 戰棋回合制 2月3日 日服新開","createTime":"2020-02-04T03:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T17:12:23.000Z","uid":84018,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0408a36c89e649ba40668584bb9668b88be47d7f","tid":1860994,"uid":84018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T03:02:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">介紹及下載</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/9558#COMMENT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F9558%23COMMENT&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=9bbb0c16\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/9558#COMMENT</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/id1475618356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1475618356&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=a3940a24\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/id1475618356</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WPJtOcYYpbQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWPJtOcYYpbQ&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=7a079c88\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WPJtOcYYpbQ</a><br />\n<br />\n《三國志英雄》是一款三國志題材的棋盤式回合制戰鬥遊戲，在遊戲中再現了三國時代的英傑們馳騁沙場的英姿。本作同時擁有桌上遊戲簡單易上手的特性和電子競技的競技性，採用將棋、圍棋等棋類遊戲玩法，在輕鬆簡單的規則下，玩家在策略上的佈置將是取得勝利的關鍵。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n#三國志Heroz #三国志ヒーローズ</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊戲玩法係調配6-10零個武將（cost ~20-25隻），計埋cost 120-150，每個武將有唔同能力，攻擊及移動方式，之後雙方 battle。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首抽：</span></strong>入Game完成教學，第一次首抽個個一樣，5星孫策（騎兵）及指定既3-4星將。<br />\n第一日登入送5星劉備（騎兵）。<br />\n之後再自己會有 1券+600-900石。拎曬去抽張飛活動包。抽唔中5星就del game data重開始。<br />\n目前有張飛（蜀盾兵），馬超（蜀騎），司馬懿（魏軍師），呂玲綺（他國弓），孫策（吳騎，開局已送）。<strong>最實用好似係張飛，馬超。</strong><br />\n不過啲武將都有4星武作代替。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n登入滿7日/或者課HK$40/打Rank會有5星交換券，可換各國一指定5星將：（有黃忠，孫權等）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BVeGNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BVeGNc.jpg&h=994f57d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MQio0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MQio0v.jpg&h=71635929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLb9vFu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLb9vFu.jpg&h=40854827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ody0Ckt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fody0Ckt.jpg&h=5395f306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下為張遼活動，但日文睇唔明點攞。<br />\n對戰打Rank。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HaoTcUe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHaoTcUe.jpg&h=fc84168e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TaRJ0V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TaRJ0V.jpg&h=8932cbe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAwhEyF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAwhEyF.jpg&h=e4d6a2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dwMBaFm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdwMBaFm.jpg&h=ffe378af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"467a66d464dab2c0dd200e5fe6888769caa07010","tid":1860994,"uid":84018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"有人玩再講。<br />\n<br />\n新game落地，光榮出版"},{"pid":"6732d4d0ebd9002f29fff5ce1d69093bd9e0efed","tid":1860994,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467a66d464dab2c0dd200e5fe6888769caa07010","tid":1860994,"uid":84018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"有人玩再講。<br />\n<br />\n新game落地，光榮出版"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"你再講我先玩"},{"pid":"a94198d9c6db285c89b5c74a83dd2e527edbca03","tid":1860994,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor